                <li>Go to the <a href="../../list-of-windows/alvao-asset-management-console/software/license-registry/edit-license/substitute-products">tab.
 Substitute products</a> and add any older versions of the product that the license may cover - or see <a href="licenses/downgrade">Enable downgrade</a>.</li>
